drm/amd/display: Interface for LTTPR interop

[WHY]
The logic to toggle LTTPR transparent/non-transparent requires 2 flags
provided by BIOS

[HOW]
Repurpose the interface to get dce caps so both LTTPR querying functions
can use them.

